OL,3,CDerby's market hall reopens after
OL,4,Cseven-year multi-million pound
OL,5,Crenovation
OL,7,FDerby's Market Hall has reopened after
OL,8,Fa seven-year #3.5-million renovation.
OL,10,FA ribbon-cutting ceremony was held on
OL,11,FSaturday morning (May 24th) - almost
OL,12,F159 years to the day since its
OL,13,Foriginal grand opening.
OL,15,FHundreds of people were seen queuing
OL,16,Foutside waiting to get inside the
OL,17,FGrade II listed building.
