OL,3,CDerby's market hall reopens after
OL,4,Cseven-year multi-million pound
OL,5,Crenovation
OL,7,FStallholders were setting up for the
OL,8,Ffirst week of trading, which began
OL,9,Ftoday (May 26th).
OL,11,FPreviously, the Market Hall often had
OL,12,Fto close to customers if there was a
OL,13,Fchance of strong winds, snow, or heavy
OL,14,Frain in case the glass windows came
OL,15,Fout of their frames.
OL,17,FThese windows have now been replaced,
OL,18,Fand the extensive structural
OL,19,Frestoration of the roof was finished
OL,20,Fin August 2022.
